rounds.response:
I will analyze the value of my current inventory and what I need to gain. I will consider what resources my opponent might need and try to make offers that are beneficial to both of us. I will prioritize trades that significantly increase my total resource value, and be open to smaller beneficial trades as well.

My current total value is:
(23 * 6) + (25 * 12) + (15 * 15) + (19 * 29) + (23 * 32)
= 138 + 300 + 225 + 551 + 736
= 1950

I will aim to increase this value. High-value resources are Ore and Brick. I have a good quantity of everything, so I can afford to offer all types of resources.

[Offer: 5 Wheat, 3 Wood -> 2 Ore]
